    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical attention; the engine runs roughly and the transmission exhibits frequent slipping. Cosmestically, the car shows its age with substantial rust on the lower body panels, significant paint oxidation, and several large dents. Inside, the cabin has seen heavy use, with torn seat upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and a non-functional air conditioning system. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a valuable source of spare parts for a similar model.",
