    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a synthesis of performance and reliability. Boasting a refined interior and a comprehensive service history, it delivers a composed driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. Every mechanical component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure sustained operational integrity and long-term value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
